cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.SD, cs.MM, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a new two-factor authentication mechanism that is usable and deployable. It uses ambient sound to verify the proximity of the user's phone to the device being used to log in. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Security (cs.CR), Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), System and Control (cs.SY), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Sound (cs.SD).
